Usage: SHOWAWAY on channels|off
  Toggles notifying when you do SETAWAY or SETBACK

  When you do SETAWAY or SETBACK client will send all the channels you
  are on notification that you're now away or that you have returned.
  It applies to auto set away too.

See also:
  AWAYT
  PLAYBACK
  REMLOG
  SETAWAY
  SETBACK
